<div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4">Welcome</h1>
    <p>The SECS/GEM ID Generator is a tool that automatically generates standardized equipment IDs, including Alarm IDs, Collection Event IDs (CEIDs), and Variable IDs (VIDs) for semiconductor manufacturing equipment following SEMI E5 and E30 standards. It uses the tool configuration and produces a consistent, organized ID set exportable as CSV or JSON, ready for direct integration into a machine's ID library. The goal is to eliminate manual ID assignment and ensure every tool ships with a standardized, spec-compliant ID structure across the fleet.</a>.</p>
